name: Ambigrammatic Figure 0252 (Card #26/55)
description: Created by Golan Levin (@golan) and Lingdong Huang (@LingdongH) with a machine learning system, this is card #26 out of 55 in the Ambigrammatic Figure Series (2020). The grotesque face in this artwork is an "ambigram": an image that is legible both upside-down and right-side-up.
